Uses Google Calendar API to register "Arriving" and "Leaving" commands per user using it. 
Fetches time from The Institute for Telecommunication Sciences's time server and syncs 
it with Google Calendar when sending the event.

Compile your code with AIR 2.0. If you want the icon, place it in the "bin-release"-directory
upon compiling to attach it with the application.

Remember to insert credentials for a Google Account, could be both Hosted or regular 
Google Account, more information inside the code.